text: SheiKra is a roller coaster located at Busch Gardens Tampa Bay in Tampa, Florida. It is a Dive Coaster which means riders experience a moment of free fall. SheiKra was the first Dive Coaster. It is floorless and features a 90 degree drop. == References == Category:Steel roller coasters Category:Roller coasters in the United States Category:Tampa, Florida Category:Roller coasters by name Category:2005 establishments in the United States Category:2000s establishments in Florida
